[Amit Varma]: This episode of The Seen and The Unseen is brought to you by Intel.

00:00:30.560 --> 00:00:35.680
[Amit Varma]: Doing long conversations, not interviews but conversations allows me to build a relaxed,

00:00:35.680 --> 00:00:41.120
[Amit Varma]: discursive flow that helps me to go to places I otherwise wouldn't. These deep dives would

00:00:41.120 --> 00:00:44.960
[Amit Varma]: not be possible in shorter formats. You can read that post for my full reasoning,

00:00:44.960 --> 00:00:49.520
