00:00:57.600 --> 00:01:02.880
[Amit Varma]: but before we speak about that, I like to speak with them about them. This humanizes them,

00:01:02.880 --> 00:01:08.000
[Amit Varma]: makes them more three-dimensional to me. I get a sense of the multitudes they contain.

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:13.040
