00:01:13.040 --> 00:01:18.560
[Amit Varma]: in which we have lived, how society has changed or not changed, and sometimes I even get insights

00:01:18.560 --> 00:01:23.440
[Amit Varma]: about my own self just by being forced to think about things I otherwise would not have thought

00:01:23.440 --> 00:01:28.960
[Amit Varma]: about. This also helps give context to whatever subject we go on to discuss. Well, in today's

00:01:28.960 --> 00:01:34.160
[Amit Varma]: episode, there is no special subject as such. My guest does host a popular podcast, but he

00:01:34.160 --> 00:01:38.640
