[Guest]: But it's impossible to, it's my, so there is this, I don't know, have you, are you familiar

02:24:41.160 --> 02:24:44.160
[Guest]: with that Bonhoeffer's theory of stupidity?

02:24:44.160 --> 02:24:45.720
[Guest]: No, please tell me.

02:24:45.720 --> 02:24:48.600
[Guest]: There's this guy named Dieter Bonhoeffer, okay.

02:24:48.600 --> 02:24:52.640
[Guest]: So Dieter Bonhoeffer was a young pastor, very touching story, actually.

02:24:52.640 --> 02:25:00.520
[Guest]: He was a very, he was a pastor, he was, you know, he like spreading the word of Christ.

02:25:00.520 --> 02:25:04.160
[Guest]: And he believed, he believed in the message of the Bible.

02:25:04.160 --> 02:25:12.840
[Guest]: So when Hitler was gaining prominence, he protested, he saw when, this is what used

02:25:12.840 --> 02:25:13.840
[Guest]: to happen, right?

02:25:13.840 --> 02:25:18.240
[Guest]: So people used to, Hitler used to say, Jews are the cause of all your problems.

02:25:18.240 --> 02:25:23.160
[Guest]: And people would go and throw stones at Jewish shops and they would do that.

02:25:23.160 --> 02:25:28.600
[Guest]: So this is way before, you know, concentration camps and all the thing.

02:25:28.600 --> 02:25:32.760
[Guest]: But you know, they used to, they used to do those things.

02:25:32.760 --> 02:25:39.400
[Guest]: And Dieter Bonhoeffer used to go and give speeches and tell people that this is wrong,

02:25:39.400 --> 02:25:40.400
[Guest]: you cannot do this.

02:25:40.400 --> 02:25:48.980
[Guest]: This is not, this is not what, and you know, a lot of the ire against Jews comes from Christian

02:25:48.980 --> 02:25:52.480
[Guest]: history about, you know, they were not kind to Christ.

02:25:52.480 --> 02:25:57.680
[Guest]: I don't know what the background is, but generally, historically, Jews, Christians hate Jews because

02:25:57.680 --> 02:26:01.960
[Guest]: of bad things that the Jews did to the Christians, so on and so forth.

02:26:01.960 --> 02:26:04.720
[Guest]: And Bonhoeffer used to say all that, anyway.

02:26:04.720 --> 02:26:13.720
[Guest]: So none of it worked, Nazism grew and eventually they, you know, they took power and World

02:26:13.720 --> 02:26:22.080
[Guest]: War started and some years after that, Bonhoeffer was like, you know, going around saying things

02:26:22.080 --> 02:26:26.520
[Guest]: and they finally arrested him and they put him in a concentration camp.

02:26:26.520 --> 02:26:33.480
[Guest]: And tragically, just two weeks before the regime collapsed, before the Allies won, Bonhoeffer

02:26:33.480 --> 02:26:41.800
[Guest]: was executed for being in on a plot to kill Hitler, which he wasn't, but they, you know,

02:26:41.800 --> 02:26:43.520
[Guest]: that happened.

02:26:43.520 --> 02:26:46.840
[Guest]: And but when he was in the prison, he wrote a book.

02:26:46.840 --> 02:26:52.480
[Guest]: The book was about stupidity and his point was stupidity is worse than malevolence because

02:26:52.480 --> 02:27:01.600
[Guest]: malevolence has an agenda and you can unmask that agenda, but stupidity has no agenda whatsoever

02:27:01.600 --> 02:27:07.720
[Guest]: and stupid people will do things to harm you which don't benefit them.

02:27:07.720 --> 02:27:09.640
[Guest]: A malevolent person will not do that.

02:27:09.640 --> 02:27:12.760
[Guest]: He will harm you only if it benefits him.

02:27:12.760 --> 02:27:21.440
[Guest]: So his basic thesis was, be very afraid of stupid people and stay away from them.

02:27:21.440 --> 02:27:26.000
[Guest]: And to some extent, I see this happening even today.

02:27:26.000 --> 02:27:31.800
[Guest]: I don't think we'll ever go into that level of extreme, but it happened all over the world.

02:27:31.800 --> 02:27:37.360
[Guest]: It happens here, it happens in the US, you have this QAnon crowd, they are just stupid

02:27:37.360 --> 02:27:49.040
[Guest]: people and you have to sort of strengthen your fellow people, people around you to recognize

02:27:49.040 --> 02:27:51.560
[Guest]: that stupidity and sort of fight against it.

02:27:51.560 --> 02:27:52.560
[Amit Varma]: Yeah.

02:27:52.560 --> 02:27:55.240
[Amit Varma]: I mean, this whole thing of stupidity being worse than malevolence reminds me of Harry

02:27:55.240 --> 02:27:56.680
[Amit Varma]: Frankfurt and bullshit.

02:27:56.680 --> 02:27:59.960
[Amit Varma]: Harry Frankfurt is a philosopher who wrote this great book called On Bullshit.

02:27:59.960 --> 02:28:03.440
[Amit Varma]: And his point was that bullshit is different from lies.

02:28:03.440 --> 02:28:08.960
[Amit Varma]: A liar appreciates that there is something that is a fact, but he deliberately lies.

02:28:08.960 --> 02:28:11.480
[Amit Varma]: Whereas a bullshitter doesn't give a shit.

02:28:11.480 --> 02:28:13.600
[Amit Varma]: So half the time he might even be right.

02:28:13.600 --> 02:28:14.600
[Amit Varma]: Right.

02:28:14.600 --> 02:28:15.600
[Amit Varma]: He is just bullshitting.

02:28:15.600 --> 02:28:19.160
[Amit Varma]: He is just making up what comes into his head to go with whatever the narrative is.

02:28:19.160 --> 02:28:21.200
[Amit Varma]: And he's not aware himself that it's true.

02:28:21.200 --> 02:28:22.200
[Amit Varma]: Yeah.

02:28:22.200 --> 02:28:27.400
[Guest]: Like Donald Trump was a classic bullshitter in that sense, that he will say anything.

02:28:27.400 --> 02:28:30.400
[Amit Varma]: And in a sense, that's more dangerous than lies.

02:28:30.400 --> 02:28:32.640
[Guest]: You cannot expose that as a lie.

02:28:32.640 --> 02:28:34.600
[Guest]: So a lie is clearly a lie.

02:28:34.600 --> 02:28:38.160
[Guest]: So you knew that it was black, but you said it's white.

02:28:38.160 --> 02:28:39.160
[Guest]: That's a lie.

02:28:39.160 --> 02:28:41.160
[Guest]: Bullshitter, he doesn't even know.

02:28:41.160 --> 02:28:42.160
[Amit Varma]: No.

02:28:42.160 --> 02:28:43.400
[Amit Varma]: And a bullshitter takes you into crazy directions.

02:28:43.400 --> 02:28:49.800
[Amit Varma]: Like there is this SSR conspiracy theory that I like to speak about, which is see the initial

02:28:49.800 --> 02:28:52.240
[Amit Varma]: SSR theories were lies, right?

02:28:52.240 --> 02:28:57.640
[Amit Varma]: The initial conspiracy theories that, you know, Rhea gave him drugs and there was all

02:28:57.640 --> 02:28:58.640
[Amit Varma]: this other shit happening.

02:28:58.640 --> 02:28:59.720
[Amit Varma]: Those were lies.

02:28:59.720 --> 02:29:00.800
[Amit Varma]: But the bullshit is crazy.

02:29:00.800 --> 02:29:04.160
[Amit Varma]: The bullshit is that he believed in something in quantum mechanics, which splits an atom

02:29:04.160 --> 02:29:05.760
[Amit Varma]: into two.

02:29:05.760 --> 02:29:07.720
[Amit Varma]: And he apparently tweeted about it once.

02:29:07.720 --> 02:29:09.880
[Amit Varma]: So he split himself into two.

02:29:09.880 --> 02:29:15.240
[Amit Varma]: And there were two SSRs and the one that died or was killed rather was a duplicate.

02:29:15.240 --> 02:29:19.880
[Amit Varma]: And the real one invented Covaxin and is in hiding somewhere because Yogi Adityanath is

02:29:19.880 --> 02:29:20.880
[Amit Varma]: looking for him.

02:29:20.880 --> 02:29:24.320
[Amit Varma]: Now, none of this is a lie and none of this is something a liar would say.

02:29:24.320 --> 02:29:29.240
[Amit Varma]: A liar would have no incentive at just going into these different crazy areas.

02:29:29.240 --> 02:29:33.200
[Amit Varma]: This is just bullshit of a very strange kind.

02:29:33.200 --> 02:29:39.200
[Amit Varma]: And, you know, just going back to the earlier point of not speaking out and, you know, more

02:29:39.200 --> 02:29:40.200
[Amit Varma]: and more.

02:29:40.200 --> 02:29:44.720
[Amit Varma]: I think that sometimes a practical attitude is not my circus, not my monkeys or as a better

02:29:44.720 --> 02:29:49.960
[Amit Varma]: way of saying this comes from the novel Kashi Kasi, which is Bhaar Mein Jaye Duniya Hum

