[Guest]: I keep telling my every time I have this conversation with different people, I mentally make a note

02:35:21.080 --> 02:35:24.160
[Guest]: that from tomorrow morning, I'm going to start that.

02:35:24.160 --> 02:35:25.560
[Amit Varma]: I've never gotten around to that.

02:35:25.560 --> 02:35:30.520
[Amit Varma]: Yeah, I downloaded the Headspace app, I downloaded Sam Harris's app and kind of paid a subscription

02:35:30.520 --> 02:35:34.480
[Amit Varma]: fee for it for a few months before this RBI regulation, it just lapsed.

02:35:34.480 --> 02:35:36.520
[Amit Varma]: I wasn't using it anyway.

02:35:36.520 --> 02:35:42.480
[Amit Varma]: But to get back to the Vipashyana, the interesting thing was because the whole exercise is that

02:35:42.480 --> 02:35:48.440
[Amit Varma]: you're observing yourself, the meal I had after that, you know, my wife would also done

02:35:48.440 --> 02:35:50.880
[Amit Varma]: the thing and it wasn't so bad for her.

